Cyalume Technologies Holdings Inc.


            
            Cyalume Technologies Holdings, Inc. operates as a holding company, which designs and manufactures tactical products and training solutions. The company manufactures chemical light, reflective and battlefield effects simulator products while its services include planning and implementing tactical training exercises simulating real-world experiences. It also sells the chemical light and reflective products into the law enforcement, commercial, and other markets. Cyalume Technologies Holdings was founded on July 19, 2005 and is headquartered in Fort Lauderdale, FL.

            
            (See Full Profile)


  



 


