Cyalume Technologies Holdings, Inc. Key Developments

Cyalume Technologies Holdings, Inc. announced delayed 10-Q filing
May 15 17
On 05/15/2017, Cyalume Technologies Holdings, Inc. announced that they will be unable to file their next 10-Q by the deadline required by the SEC.


Cyalume Technologies Holdings, Inc. and Cyalume Technologies, Inc. Appoint Andrea Settembrino as Chief Financial Officer
Nov 3 16
Effective as of October 28, 2016, Cyalume Technologies Holdings, Inc. appointed Andrea Settembrino as the company's new Chief Financial Officer. Ms. Settembrino has been the company's Corporate Controller since July 2013. Prior to joining the company, from 2009 to 2013, Ms. Settembrino was the Vice President of Finance at eDiets.com, Inc. Settembrino will serve as Chief Financial Officer of the company and Cyalume Technologies, Inc.


Cyalume Technologies Holdings, Inc. Announces the Retirement of Michael Bielonko as Chief Financial Officer
Jul 18 16
On July 15, 2016, Cyalume Technologies Holdings, Inc. announced that Michael Bielonko, Chief Financial Officer of the company has retired from his position with the company.


