Company Overview of Cyalume Specialty Products, Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Cyalume Specialty Products, Inc., a life-sciences and specialty chemical technology company, engages in the research, development, and manufacture of pharmaceutical ingredients and applied materials. The company’s products include non-pharmaceutical products, cosmetic ingredients, nutritional supplements, and polymers and monomers. It also offers custom synthesis, toll manufacturing, process optimization, method development, lyophilization, reaction, and laboratory services. The company was formerly known as JFC Technologies, LLC and changed its name to Cyalume Specialty Products, Inc., as a result of its acquisition by Cyalume Technologies Holdings, Inc. Cyalume Specialty Products, Inc. was...
Cyalume Specialty Products, Inc., a life-sciences and specialty chemical technology company, engages in the research, development, and manufacture of pharmaceutical ingredients and applied materials. The company’s products include non-pharmaceutical products, cosmetic ingredients, nutritional supplements, and polymers and monomers. It also offers custom synthesis, toll manufacturing, process optimization, method development, lyophilization, reaction, and laboratory services. The company was formerly known as JFC Technologies, LLC and changed its name to Cyalume Specialty Products, Inc., as a result of its acquisition by Cyalume Technologies Holdings, Inc. Cyalume Specialty Products, Inc. was founded in 1970 and is based in Bound Brook, New Jersey. As of September 1, 2011, Cyalume Specialty Products, Inc. operates as a subsidiary of Cyalume Technologies Holdings, Inc.
